OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night to come with spells
OL,7,Fof rain and drizzle. Some misty low
OL,8,Fcloud developing. Fresh to strong
OL,9,Fsoutheasterly winds easing later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FVariable cloud and bright
OL,12,Fspells for Orkney with some showery
OL,13,Frain at times, but some drier
OL,14,Finterludes too. Cloudy throughout the
OL,15,Fday across Shetland with a chance of
OL,16,Fhaar.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
