OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly dry on Thursday, a few light
OL,7,Fafternoon showers spreading north.
OL,8,FRain at times on Friday, drier later.
OL,9,FChance of some rain at first on
OL,10,FSaturday, otherwise mainly dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
